text: Tascina is a genus of moths within the Castniidae family. It is found in South East Asia. ==Selected species== *Tascina dalattensis Fukuda, 2000 *Tascina orientalis Westwood, 1877 *Tascina metallica Pagenstecher, 1890 *Tascina nicevillei (Hampson, 1895) ==External links== *Moths of Borneo Category:Castniidae
